                    <div class="content text-center">
                        <h3 class="ddd">Infrastructure</h3>
                          <p>A resilient and distributed infrastructure with dedicated CDNs, worldwide mirrors and IPFS/P2P gateways to give access to software and information even to people in totalitarian regimes or in poor countries where stable internet connection to foreign countries is not an option.</p>
